summary: An Ordinance providing for the purchase of Block Five (5), Joseph C. Kinnear's Addition to the City of Seattle, for park and parkway purposes, for a sum not to exceed Fifteen Thousand Dollars ($15,000.00), payment to be made from the Park Fund of the City of Seattle, payable, Two Thousand Dollars ($2,000.00) cash, and balance within six months, with interest at 5%.
